---
import MarketingLayout from '../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Book a thirty-minute review with five of your live contracts. We will show you what your current CLM is missing."
>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="section" style="padding-top: clamp(56px, 6vw, 100px); padding-bottom: clamp(28px, 3vw, 48px);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 items-baseline">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
        <div class="label label-ink">Contact</div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
        <h1 class="display display-xl" style="margin-top: 12px;">
          Bring five contracts. <span class="emph">Bring questions.</span><br/>
          We will bring findings.
        </h1>
        <p class="lead" style="margin-top: 24px; max-width: 640px;">
          A thirty-minute walkthrough with your real documents. No slides, no procurement involvement, no NDA required. Findings are yours to keep regardless of whether you proceed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FORM + INFO -->
<section class="section sr" id="form" style="background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-10 gap-y-10">

      <!-- Form -->
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="label label-ink" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Get in touch</div>
        <h2 class="display display-md" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">Drop us a note.</h2>

        <form action="mailto:sales@evaluetor.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" style="display: grid; gap: 18px;">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2" style="gap: 18px;">
            <div>
              <label class="label" for="name">Your name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="fld" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="label" for="email">Work email</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="fld" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2" style="gap: 18px;">
            <div>
              <label class="label" for="company">Company</label>
              <input type="text" id="company" name="company" required class="fld" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="label" for="role">Role</label>
              <input type="text" id="role" name="role" placeholder="e.g. Procurement Director" class="fld" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="label" for="message">What are you dealing with?</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="A few sentences about your portfolio, where you suspect leakage, or just what you want to see." class="fld"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 6px;">
            <button type="submit" class="cta-btn">Send <span class="arr">→</span></button>
            <span class="ink-3" style="font-size: 13px;">Or email <a href="mailto:sales@evaluetor.com" class="a-orange" style="font-size: 13px;">sales@evaluetor.com</a> directly.</span>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Info column -->
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5">
        <div style="border: 1px solid var(--rule-2); padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 18px;">
          <div class="label label-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">What a review looks like</div>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
            <li style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-2); font-size: 14.5px;"><span class="mono ink-3" style="font-size: 11px; margin-right: 10px;">01</span>You bring five live contracts. Any format.</li>
            <li style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-2); font-size: 14.5px;"><span class="mono ink-3" style="font-size: 11px; margin-right: 10px;">02</span>We extract obligations, SLAs, risk patterns, renewals.</li>
            <li style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-2); font-size: 14.5px;"><span class="mono ink-3" style="font-size: 11px; margin-right: 10px;">03</span>Findings are scored against portfolio norms — live.</li>
            <li style="padding: 10px 0; font-size: 14.5px;"><span class="mono ink-3" style="font-size: 11px; margin-right: 10px;">04</span>You keep the findings, regardless of next steps.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="border: 1px solid var(--rule-2); padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 18px;">
          <div class="label label-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Office</div>
          <p class="ink-2" style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 500;">Evaluetor B.V.</p>
          <p class="ink-3" style="font-size: 14px;">the Netherlands</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border: 1px solid var(--rule-2); padding: 28px;">
          <div class="label label-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Direct line</div>
          <a href="mailto:sales@evaluetor.com" class="a-orange" style="font-size: 15px;">sales@evaluetor.com <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  .fld {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding: 11px 14px;
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-2);
    font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: border-color .15s ease, background .15s ease;
  }
  .fld:focus {
    outline: none;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-color: var(--orange-2);
  }
  .fld::placeholder { color: var(--ink-4); }
  textarea.fld { resize: vertical; }
</style>

</MarketingLayout>
